{"tid":1551494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中環遮打花園下午1:30有遊行集會 往美國駐港總領事館遞信          中聯辦保安未見加強","createTime":"2019-09-08T04:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:52:19.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b6390a11e7731c2c503a28ef9234fff05e83b268","tid":1551494,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"逆權運動】中環下午有遊行集會 中聯辦保安未見加強<br />\n<br />\n有網民發起今日在中環遮打花園舉行「香港人權與民主祈禱會」，並於下午2時半遊行往美國駐港總領事館遞交「香港人權與民主宣言」聯署信。距離美國駐港總領事館約3公里的中聯辦依舊架設了水馬，國徽沒有「包膠」，保安亦沒有特別嚴密，今日早上附近一帶氣氛平靜。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"142f9719ce01d42c726cc501157aede2d33ead10","tid":1551494,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:38:52.000Z","msg":"今日係和理非非"},{"pid":"34cbc7ff542c93fb0b372930282ba2e55327d694","tid":1551494,"uid":7971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"今日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱fuck the popo <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱毅進仔<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱今天我 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日係唱The Star-Spangled Banner</span>🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一定一定要係國際媒體面前一齊全民大合唱啊<br />\n點都要唱到第一段啊！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<del>因為全首太長</del><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟第一段</span><br />\nOh, say can you see by the dawn's early light<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed at the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\nWhose broad stripes and bright stars thru the perilous fight,<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched were so gallantly streaming?<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare, the bombs bursting in air,<br />\nGave proof through the night that our flag was still there.<br />\nOh, say does that star-spangled banner yet wave<br />\nO'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟第一段</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫英文口號</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Five demands Not one less</span><br />\n香港警察 知法犯法<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Hong Kong Police breaking the peace</span><br />\n與港同在 促成人權法案<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Stand with Hong Kong, pass the democracy act</span><br />\n為自由抗爭 制度已失衡<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Fight for freedom, no faith in the systems</span> </strong>"},{"pid":"d88aa0397ea102e7f08ac769b7d605c0c3b50308","tid":1551494,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">警會冇權傳召證人</div></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cr8vCI9d8uM&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCr8vCI9d8uM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkpriK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=25786eea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cr8vCI9d8uM&amp;feature=youtu.be</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫人推埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">3分鐘了解香港人權與民主法案</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1551225/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1551225/page/1</a></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=